Package com.nabto.api

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NabtoAndroidAssetManager
    Handles the Nabto assets used by the NabtoApi on Android.
    NabtoApi
    Nabto client API.
    NabtoCApiWrapper  
    NabtoClient
    The NabtoClient is a simple way to communicate with a Nabto device.
    NabtoDefaultAssetManager
    Handles the Nabto assets used by the NabtoApi.
    RpcResult
    Result object of the functions NabtoApi.rpcSetDefaultInterface(String, Session), NabtoApi.rpcSetInterface(String, String, Session), and NabtoApi.rpcInvoke(String, Session).
    Session
    Result object of the function NabtoApi.openSession(String, String) or NabtoApi.openSessionBare().
    Stream
    Result object of the function NabtoApi.streamOpen(String, Session).
    StreamReadResult
    Result object of the function NabtoApi.streamRead(Stream).
    Tunnel
    Result object of the function NabtoApi.tunnelOpenTcp(int, String, String, int, Session).
    TunnelInfoResult
    Result object of the function NabtoApi.tunnelInfo(Tunnel).
    UrlResult
    Result object of the functions NabtoApi.fetchUrl(String, Session), and NabtoApi.submitPostData(String, byte[], String, Session).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NabtoConnectionType
    The NabtoConnectionType enumeration is telling the underlying connection type for a stream.
    NabtoStatus
    The NabtoStatus enumeration is the set of status values that most of the functions in the Client API return.
    NabtoStreamOption
    The NabtoStreamOption enumeration is listing the valid options that can be applied to a nabto stream.
    NabtoTunnelState
    The NabtoTunnelState enumeration is telling the state of the tunnel and the underlying connection type for a stream carrying the tunnel.
